➜推荐 | 来锡林郭勒草原，给你点“颜色”看看
http://www.sohu.com/a/420115570_645092	37860
<p class="ql-align-center">首先</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">请大家伸出自己的小手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在离十一中秋假期还有这一手的时间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">终于可以数着手指头算假期了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闲时无计划，忙时多费力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">现在就是计划行程的日子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋色正浓，怎能在家里度此佳期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然你也可以不用计划</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就来锡林郭勒草原</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让我给你点“颜色”看看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200922/6dad9d49f7cf494499bfe7b231cf73be.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">摄影/嘎·巴特尔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>黄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋草、秋叶、秋天的黄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200922/a6eb4b321e0c405b8b446063769fc1d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
